testHelp

Class GenericObjectAssertionBase<T,AssertionT>

  • Object
    • GenericObjectAssertionBase<T,AssertionT>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the object type, for storing object to be examined
    AssertionT - the assertion type, for downcasting returned this
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericExceptionAssertion, GenericObjectAssertion, StringAssertion

    public abstract class GenericObjectAssertionBase<T,AssertionT>
extends Object
    Abstract base class for assertion classes for object (as opposed to primitive) types. It implements covariance of subclass assertion return types via a generic type argument. The only abstract method is getDftDesc(), which simplifies initialization of field DFT_DESC.

    Note: this class is a genericized version of the reusable functionality in class ObjectAssertion.

    Author:
    John Armstrong
